-- MOVES-Mizuho Bank hires John Castanon from MUFG Union Bank
-- 
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 04:18PM EDT
-- None



Sept 17 (Reuters) - Mizuho Bank, a unit of Japan-based Mizuho Financial Group Inc <8411.T>, appointed John Castanon as a director in its public finance investment banking group.

He will be based in New York, reporting to Bran Raskovic, managing director and head of public finance.